    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Chapter 15:Dynamic Promramming]]></title>
    <link href="http://iceout.github.com/blog/2012/08/27/chapter-15-dynamic-promramming/"/>
    <updated>2012-08-27T10:19:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://iceout.github.com/blog/2012/08/27/chapter-15-dynamic-promramming</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>动态规划的4个步骤:</p>

<ol>
  <li>找到最优子结构</li>
  <li>递归定义最优解</li>
  <li>按自底向上的方式计算最优解的值</li>
  <li>由计算结果构造一个最优解</li>
</ol>

<p>15.1-2
可以用归纳法</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display"> \because r_1(n) = r_2(n) = 1 = 2^0 = 2^{n-n}; r_1(j) = r_2(j) = r_1(j+1) + r_2(j+1) </script>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display"> \therefore r_1(n-1) =  r_1(n) + r_2(n) = 2 = 2^1 </script>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display"> \forall k, r_1(n-k) = r_2(n-k) = 2^k; </script>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display"> r_1(n-k-1) = r_2(n-k-1) = r_1(n-k) + r_2(n-k) = 2^k + 2^K = 2^{k+1} </script>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display"> r_i(n-k-1) = 2^{k+1} </script>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display"> r_i(j) = 2^{n-j} </script>

<p>15.1-4
<script type="math/tex">f_i[j]</script>的值只与<script type="math/tex">f_i[j-1]</script>相关,所以可以从$2n$缩减为$2$个._</p>

<p>15.2-2</p>

<pre><code>MATRIX-CHAIN-MULTIPLY(A, s, i, j)
    if i &lt; j
        x = MATRIX-CHAIN-MULTIPLY(A, s, s(i,j), j)
        y = MATRIX-CHAIN-MULTIPLY(A, s, s(i,j)+1, j)
        return MATRIX-MULTIPLY(x, y)
    else
        return Ai
</code></pre>

